universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant BaldEagle : obj
constant Bear : obj
constant Cat : obj
constant Squirrel : obj

constant Chases : obj → obj → Prop
constant Blue : obj → Prop
constant Round : obj → Prop
constant Young : obj → Prop
constant Rough : obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Likes : obj → obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Chases BaldEagle Cat
axiom T2 : ¬ Blue BaldEagle
axiom T3 : Round BaldEagle
axiom T4 : Young BaldEagle
axiom T5 : Chases Bear Squirrel
axiom T6 : Rough Bear
axiom T7 : Sees Bear BaldEagle
axiom T8 : ¬ Sees Bear Cat
axiom T9 : Young Cat
axiom T10 : Likes Cat Bear
axiom T11 : Sees Cat Bear
axiom T12 : Sees Cat Squirrel
axiom T13 : Chases Squirrel BaldEagle
axiom T14 : Blue Squirrel
axiom T15 : Sees Squirrel BaldEagle
axiom T16 : Sees Squirrel Bear

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Squirrel → Chases x Bear
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Likes x Cat → Chases Cat Squirrel
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Bear ∧ Sees x BaldEagle → Likes x BaldEagle
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Bear ∧ Likes Bear BaldEagle → Chases x Squirrel
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Likes x Cat ∧ Sees x Squirrel → Sees Cat Squirrel
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Young x → Chases x BaldEagle
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Cat → Young Cat
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x BaldEagle ∧ Likes x BaldEagle → Round x
axiom R9 : Sees BaldEagle Bear → Likes BaldEagle Bear

theorem squirrel_likes_bald_eagle : Likes Squirrel BaldEagle :=
begin
  apply R3 Squirrel,
  split,
  exact R1 Squirrel T13,
  exact T15,
end
